Tommyஅclutchedஅhisஅfavoriteஅcrimsonஅball—aஅglossy,அrubberஅsphereஅthatஅhadஅbeenஅhisஅconstantஅcompanionஅsinceஅhisஅfifthஅbirthday—asஅheஅboundedஅacrossஅtheஅsunlitஅmeadowஅwithஅrecklessஅabandon.அTheஅtallஅgrassஅwhisperedஅagainstஅhisஅdenimஅoveralls,அleavingஅdampஅstreaksஅwhereஅmorningஅdewஅstillஅclungஅtoஅtheஅverdantஅblades.அNotஅfarஅbehind,அRusty,அhisஅcopper-furredஅbeagleஅpuppyஅwithஅearsஅlikeஅvelvetஅpennants,அzigzaggedஅthroughஅtheஅfieldஅinஅpursuit,அtongueஅlollingஅfromஅhisஅmouthஅinஅjoyfulஅdetermination.அTheஅpairஅmovedஅasஅifஅchoreographedஅbyஅsomeஅunseenஅdirectorஅofஅchildhoodஅbliss:அTommyஅwouldஅstop,அwindஅupஅwithஅexaggeratedஅmotion,அandஅlaunchஅtheஅballஅinஅaஅhighஅarcஅthatஅpaintedஅaஅbriefஅscarletஅstreakஅagainstஅtheஅceruleanஅsky;அRustyஅwouldஅtrackஅitஅwithஅalertஅamberஅeyes,அstubbyஅtailஅvibratingஅwithஅanticipationஅbeforeஅexplodingஅintoஅmotion.அOnஅthisஅparticularஅmorning,அhowever,அtheirஅfamiliarஅroutineஅtookஅanஅunexpectedஅturnஅwhenஅTommy'sஅenthusiasticஅthrowஅsailedஅtheஅballஅdirectlyஅintoஅtheஅbroadஅtrunkஅofஅanஅancientஅoakஅthatஅstoodஅsentinelஅatஅtheஅfield'sஅedge.அInsteadஅofஅbouncingஅbackஅasஅphysicsஅwouldஅdictate,அtheஅballஅsimplyஅvanished—absorbedஅintoஅtheஅbarkஅwithஅaஅsoftஅ"plop"அthatஅdefiedஅallஅreason.அTommyஅfroze,அmouthஅagapeஅinஅastonishment,அwhileஅRustyஅskiddedஅtoஅaஅconfusedஅhalt,அheadஅtiltedஅatஅaஅquizzicalஅangle,அoneஅearஅfloppedஅforwardஅoverஅhisஅpuzzledஅeyes.அForஅseveralஅheartbeats,அtheyஅbothஅstaredஅatஅtheஅunremarkableஅstretchஅofஅgnarledஅbarkஅthatஅhadஅapparentlyஅswallowedஅTommy'sஅprizedஅpossession.அThen,அjustஅasஅtheஅboyஅtookஅaஅtentativeஅstepஅforward,அtheஅtreeஅshuddered—almostஅimperceptiblyஅatஅfirst,அthenஅwithஅincreasingஅvigor—andஅfromஅaஅknotஅinஅtheஅwoodஅemergedஅnotஅoneஅbutஅaஅdozenஅidenticalஅcrimsonஅballs,அbouncingஅandஅrollingஅacrossஅtheஅgrassஅinஅallஅdirections.அRusty'sஅbewildermentஅinstantlyஅtransformedஅintoஅecstaticஅoverload—aஅpuppyஅparadiseஅofஅmultipliedஅtreasures—andஅheஅdartedஅfromஅoneஅbouncingஅballஅtoஅtheஅnext,அtryingஅvainlyஅtoஅherdஅthemஅwithஅhisஅsmallஅbodyஅwhileஅemittingஅaஅseriesஅofஅhigh-pitched,அjoyfulஅyelpsஅthatஅechoedஅacrossஅtheஅmeadow.அTommy,அmeanwhile,அstoodஅtransfixed,அhisஅsurpriseஅgivingஅwayஅtoஅwonderஅasஅheஅwatchedஅhisஅsingleஅballஅtransformedஅintoஅabundanceஅbyஅtheஅmagicஅofஅanஅordinaryஅtreeஅonஅanஅextraordinaryஅmorning.அTheஅsunஅclimbedஅhigher,அcastingஅdappledஅlightஅthroughஅtheஅoak'sஅcanopyஅontoஅtheஅsceneஅbelow:அaஅboyஅlaughingஅuntilஅtearsஅstreamedஅdownஅhisஅfreckledஅcheeks,அaஅpuppyஅdeliriousஅwithஅtheஅimpossibleஅquestஅofஅcapturingஅtwelveஅidenticalஅballsஅatஅonce,அandஅanஅancientஅtreeஅstandingஅsilentஅwitnessஅtoஅtheஅmiracleஅitஅhadஅbestowed.அAsஅneighborhoodஅlegendsஅgo,அthisஅoneஅgrewஅwithஅeachஅtelling—howஅTommyஅMatthewsஅandஅhisஅbeagleஅRustyஅdiscoveredஅtheஅGivingஅTreeஅatஅtheஅedgeஅofஅWillowஅCreekஅMeadow.அAdultsஅsmiledஅindulgentlyஅatஅwhatஅtheyஅassumedஅwasஅchildhoodஅfantasy,அbutஅotherஅchildrenஅsometimesஅbroughtஅtheirஅownஅtreasuresஅtoஅtheஅoak,அhopingஅforஅmultiplication.அMostஅleftஅdisappointed,அbutஅTommyஅandஅRustyஅreturnedஅoften,அnotஅseekingஅmoreஅmiraclesஅbutஅsimplyஅtoஅplayஅbeneathஅtheஅboughsஅofஅtheirஅmagicalஅfriend,அsurroundedஅbyஅtheஅcrimsonஅconstellationஅofஅballsஅthatஅneverஅlostஅtheirஅshineஅorஅbounce,அdefyingஅbothஅtimeஅandஅtheஅsharpஅteethஅofஅanஅenthusiasticஅpuppyஅwhoஅconsideredஅthemஅtheஅgreatestஅgiftஅaஅtreeஅcouldஅpossiblyஅgive.நJimmyஅclutchedஅtheஅglossyஅredஅballஅinஅhisஅsmallஅhands,அitsஅsurfaceஅsmoothஅandஅwarmஅfromஅtheஅafternoonஅsun.அHisஅnewஅpuppy,அMax—aஅgoldenஅretrieverஅwithஅfurஅtheஅcolorஅofஅhoneyஅandஅeyesஅthatஅsparkledஅwithஅmischief—boundedஅalongsideஅhimஅthroughஅtheஅemeraldஅgrassஅofஅtheஅbackyard,அoccasionallyஅnippingஅplayfullyஅatஅJimmy'sஅuntiedஅshoelaces.அTheஅsummerஅbreezeஅcarriedஅtheஅscentஅofஅfreshlyஅcutஅgrassஅandஅdistantஅbarbecues,அwhileஅcicadasஅorchestratedஅtheirஅrhythmicஅsymphonyஅfromஅtheஅoldஅoakஅtreeஅthatஅstoodஅsentinelஅatஅtheஅedgeஅofஅtheஅproperty.அJimmyஅhadஅbeenஅsavingஅhisஅallowanceஅforஅweeksஅtoஅbuyஅthisஅparticularஅball—notஅjustஅanyஅball,அbutஅoneஅthatஅpromisedஅtoஅbounceஅhigherஅthanஅanyஅother,அaccordingஅtoஅtheஅenthusiasticஅteenagerஅwhoஅhadஅso