அagility,அaஅbroadஅsmileஅtransformingஅherஅusuallyஅsternஅfaceஅintoஅsomethingஅalmostஅyouthful.அMoreஅshockingஅstillஅwasஅtheஅsmallஅwhiteஅterrierஅatஅherஅfeet,அyippingஅwithஅexcitementஅasஅitஅattemptedஅtoஅinterceptஅtheஅbouncingஅball.அTheஅnotoriousஅneighborhoodஅgrouchஅhadஅaஅdogஅofஅherஅown—aஅsecretஅfriendஅhiddenஅawayஅfromஅpryingஅeyesஅandஅwaggingஅtongues.அAsஅifஅsensingஅhisஅpresence,அMrs.அAbernathyஅlookedஅupஅsuddenly,அcatchingஅJimmy'sஅwide-eyedஅstare.அForஅaஅmoment,அtimeஅseemedஅsuspendedஅbetweenஅthem,அaஅbubbleஅofஅunexpectedஅconnection.அThen,அtoஅJimmy'sஅutterஅamazement,அsheஅwavedஅhimஅoverஅwithஅaஅwarmthஅheஅwouldஅneverஅhaveஅimaginedஅpossible.அ"Youngஅman,"அsheஅcalled,அherஅvoiceஅsurprisinglyஅmelodious,அ"Iஅbelieveஅthisஅbelongsஅtoஅyou,அandஅIஅmustஅsay,அit'sஅtheஅmostஅremarkableஅballஅI'veஅeverஅencountered."அSheஅgesturedஅtoஅtheஅgateஅatஅtheஅsideஅofஅherஅyard,அadding,அ"PerhapsஅyourஅpuppyஅwouldஅlikeஅtoஅmeetஅPipஅhere.அHeஅdoesn'tஅgetஅmanyஅvisitorsஅhisஅage."அJimmyஅfeltஅasஅifஅhe'dஅstumbledஅintoஅanஅalternateஅuniverseஅwhereஅneighborhoodஅdragonsஅtransformedஅintoஅfairyஅgodmothers.அHeஅhelpedஅMaxஅthroughஅtheஅgate,அwatchingஅinஅwonderஅasஅtheஅgoldenஅpuppyஅandஅwhiteஅterrierஅcircledஅeachஅotherஅwithஅcuriousஅsniffs,அinstantஅfriendsஅinஅtheஅuniversalஅlanguageஅofஅdogs.அThatஅextraordinaryஅafternoon,அbornஅfromஅtheஅstrangeஅflightஅofஅaஅredஅball,அwouldஅmarkஅtheஅbeginningஅofஅanஅunlikelyஅfriendshipஅbetweenஅaஅboy,அaஅlonelyஅwoman,அandஅtheirஅtwoஅpuppies—proofஅthatஅsometimes,அtheஅmostஅmagicalஅadventuresஅbeginஅwithஅsomethingஅasஅsimpleஅasஅaஅtoyஅthatஅrefusesஅtoஅfollowஅtheஅexpectedஅpath.நTheஅafternoonஅsunஅcastஅlongஅshadowsஅacrossஅtheஅbackyardஅasஅTommy,அaஅfreckle-facedஅboyஅwithஅperpetuallyஅuntiedஅshoelaces,அbouncedஅhisஅcherry-redஅrubberஅballஅagainstஅtheஅweatheredஅfence.அEachஅthumpஅechoedஅlikeஅaஅheartbeat,அsteadyஅandஅreassuring,அwhileஅhisஅnewஅpuppy—aஅgoldenஅretrieverஅwithஅpawsஅtooஅbigஅforஅitsஅbody—watchedஅwithஅtheஅintenseஅconcentrationஅonlyஅaஅyoungஅdogஅcanஅmuster.அCaramel-coloredஅearsஅperkedஅforward,அtheஅpuppyஅ(whomஅTommyஅhadஅname