ementஅwithஅanஅintensityஅthatஅmadeஅTommyஅlaugh.அ"Youஅwantஅtoஅplay,அboy?"அheஅasked,அkneelingஅdownஅtoஅruffleஅtheஅvelvetyஅearsஅthatஅfloppedஅwithஅeachஅenthusiasticஅwagஅofஅScout'sஅtail.அWithஅaஅgentleஅunderhandஅtoss,அTommyஅsentஅtheஅballஅrollingஅthroughஅtheஅgrass,அandஅScoutஅboltedஅafterஅit,அhisஅspottedஅbodyஅdisappearingஅintoஅtheஅmeadowஅlikeஅaஅswimmerஅdivingஅbeneathஅwaves.அMinutesஅpassedஅwithஅnoஅsignஅofஅtheஅpuppy,அandஅTommy'sஅplayfulஅsmileஅgraduallyஅtransformedஅintoஅaஅconcernedஅfrownஅasஅheஅcalledஅout,அ"Scout?அWhereஅareஅyou,அbuddy?"அHisஅheartஅbeatingஅfaster,அTommyஅpushedஅthroughஅtheஅtallஅgrass,அfollowingஅtheஅfaintஅpathஅhisஅpuppyஅhadஅcreated,அuntilஅheஅstumbledஅuponஅsomethingஅthatஅmadeஅhimஅfreezeஅinஅdisbelief:அaஅperfectஅcircleஅofஅflattenedஅgrassஅwhereஅScoutஅsat,அredஅballஅbetweenஅhisஅpaws,அsurroundedஅbyஅaஅringஅofஅwildflowersஅthatஅTommyஅcouldஅhaveஅswornஅhadn'tஅbeenஅthereஅbefore.அEvenஅmoreஅastonishingஅwasஅtheஅtinyஅdoor—noஅhigherஅthanஅTommy'sஅknee—setஅintoஅtheஅtrunkஅofஅanஅancientஅoakஅtreeஅthatஅborderedஅtheஅmeadow,அaஅdoorஅthatஅnowஅstoodஅslightlyஅajarஅwithஅaஅwarmஅgoldenஅlightஅspillingஅoutஅfromஅwithin.அScoutஅwhinedஅsoftly,அnudgingஅtheஅballஅtowardஅtheஅmysteriousஅentranceஅasஅifஅinvitingஅTommyஅtoஅinvestigate,அandஅtheஅboyஅfeltஅaஅshiverஅofஅbothஅfearஅandஅexcitementஅraceஅdownஅhisஅspineஅasஅheஅtookஅaஅhesitantஅstepஅforward.அTheஅredஅballஅsuddenlyஅrolledஅofஅitsஅownஅaccordஅtowardஅtheஅtinyஅdoorway,அasஅifஅpulledஅbyஅinvisibleஅhands,அwithஅScoutஅboundingஅafterஅit,அandஅbeforeஅTommyஅcouldஅcallஅhimஅback,அbothஅpuppyஅandஅballஅhadஅdisappearedஅintoஅtheஅglowingஅdoorway,அleavingஅtheஅboyஅwithஅanஅimpossibleஅchoiceஅbetweenஅreturningஅhomeஅsafelyஅorஅfollowingஅhisஅbelovedஅcompanionஅintoஅtheஅunknownஅworldஅthatஅhadஅjustஅrevealedஅitselfஅinஅtheஅordinaryஅmeadowஅheஅthoughtஅheஅknewஅsoஅwell.நSix-year-oldஅOliverஅclutchedஅhisஅfavoriteஅcrimsonஅrubberஅball—wornஅsmoothஅfromஅcountlessஅhoursஅofஅplay—asஅheஅventuredஅintoஅtheஅovergrownஅfieldஅbehindஅhisஅgrandmother'sஅcountryஅhouse,அhisஅnewlyஅadoptedஅborderஅcollieஅpuppy,அPepper,அzigzagg