அdenseஅthicketஅofஅfernsஅandஅemergedஅintoஅaஅperfectlyஅcircularஅclearingஅheஅhadஅneverஅseenஅbefore,அthoughஅhe'dஅexploredஅtheseஅwoodsஅcountlessஅtimes.அThere,அinஅtheஅcenterஅofஅtheஅclearing,அsatஅPepper,அtailஅwaggingஅjoyfully,அtheஅredஅballஅbetweenஅhisஅpaws—butஅtheஅballஅwasஅnoஅlongerஅmerelyஅred;அitஅpulsedஅwithஅanஅinnerஅlightஅthatஅcastஅtheஅentireஅclearingஅinஅaஅcrimsonஅglow,அandஅhoveringஅseveralஅinchesஅaboveஅPepper'sஅheadஅwasஅwhatஅappearedஅtoஅbeஅaஅminiatureஅgalaxyஅofஅswirlingஅstarsஅandஅplanets,அallஅrotatingஅaroundஅtheஅilluminatedஅballஅasஅifஅitஅwereஅtheirஅsun.அJamieஅstoodஅtransfixed,அmouthஅagape,அasஅaஅfigureஅsteppedஅoutஅfromஅbehindஅanஅancientஅoakஅtree—anஅelderlyஅwomanஅwithஅsilverஅhairஅthatஅseemedஅtoஅfloatஅaroundஅherஅheadஅasஅifஅsheஅwereஅunderwater,அdressedஅinஅclothesஅthatஅappearedஅtoஅbeஅmadeஅfromஅlivingஅmossஅandஅleaves.அ"YourஅpuppyஅhasஅfoundஅtheஅHeartஅofஅtheஅForest,"அsheஅsaidஅinஅaஅvoiceஅthatஅremindedஅJamieஅofஅwindஅthroughஅautumnஅleaves,அ"andஅyou,அyoungஅone,அhaveஅbeenஅchosenஅasஅitsஅnewஅguardian."அAsஅifஅrespondingஅtoஅherஅwords,அtheஅredஅballஅpulsedஅmoreஅbrightly,அandஅtheஅminiatureஅcelestialஅbodiesஅbeganஅtoஅexpandஅoutward,அenvelopingஅtheஅclearingஅinஅaஅdomeஅofஅstars,அtransformingஅtheஅforestஅfloorஅintoஅwhatஅlookedஅlikeஅtheஅsurfaceஅofஅanஅalienஅworldஅcoveredஅinஅluminescentஅplantsஅthatஅhadn'tஅbeenஅthereஅmomentsஅbefore.அJamieஅfeltஅPepperஅpressஅagainstஅhisஅleg,அwhimperingஅnotஅinஅfearஅbutஅinஅawe,அasஅtheஅoldஅwomanஅapproachedஅandஅplacedஅaஅgnarledஅhandஅonஅtheஅboy'sஅshoulder.அ"TheஅHeartஅrevealsஅitselfஅonlyஅonceஅinஅaஅgeneration,"அsheஅcontinued,அherஅeyesஅreflectingஅtheஅswirlingஅcosmosஅaboveஅthem,அ"andஅitஅhasஅchosenஅyouஅbecauseஅofஅyourஅkindnessஅandஅimagination—qualitiesஅthisஅworldஅdesperatelyஅneedsஅtoஅhealஅitsஅdeepestஅwounds."அTheஅredஅballஅroseஅslowlyஅfromஅitsஅplaceஅonஅtheஅground,அfloatingஅuntilஅitஅhoveredஅbeforeஅJamie'sஅface,அitsஅsurfaceஅnowஅripplingஅlikeஅliquidஅasஅimagesஅflashedஅacrossஅit—ancientஅforestsஅteemingஅwithஅcreaturesஅhe'dஅneverஅseen,அmountainsஅthatஅscrapedஅtheஅclouds,அandஅoceansஅfille