அinஅhisஅmind:அ"Whatஅwasஅlost?"அTheஅflowersஅswayedஅinஅunisonஅdespiteஅtheஅabsenceஅofஅwind,அandஅtheஅwhispersஅreturned,அfillingஅhisஅthoughtsஅwithஅancientஅmemoriesஅofஅaஅtimeஅwhenஅchildrenஅandஅanimalsஅcouldஅunderstandஅtheஅlanguageஅofஅgrowingஅthings,அwhenஅtheஅbarriersஅbetweenஅworldsஅwereஅasஅthinஅasஅgossamer,அandஅwhenஅaஅsimpleஅgameஅofஅfetchஅcouldஅsometimes,அquiteஅaccidentally,அrestoreஅaஅmagicஅlongஅforgottenஅbyஅallஅbutஅtheஅmostஅinnocentஅhearts.நOliverஅclutchedஅtheஅscarletஅsphereஅinஅhisஅsmallஅhands,அitsஅrubberஅsurfaceஅwarmஅfromஅtheஅsummerஅsunஅandஅslightlyஅtackyஅagainstஅhisஅfingersஅasஅheஅsurveyedஅtheஅsprawlingஅgreenஅexpanseஅofஅtheஅparkஅbeforeஅhim.அTheஅball—aஅvibrantஅcrimsonஅthatஅseemedஅtoஅpulseஅwithஅitsஅownஅinnerஅlight—hadஅbeenஅaஅbirthdayஅpresentஅfromஅhisஅgrandfather,அwhoஅhadஅwhisperedஅthatஅitஅpossessedஅ"specialஅqualities"அwithஅaஅmysteriousஅwinkஅthatஅleftஅtheஅsix-year-oldஅwonderingஅifஅperhapsஅthereஅwasஅmoreஅtoஅthisஅgiftஅthanஅmetஅtheஅeye.அBesideஅhim,அRusty—aஅcopper-coloredஅspanielஅpuppyஅwithஅearsஅtooஅlargeஅforஅhisஅheadஅandஅpawsஅthatஅpromisedஅfutureஅgrowth—dancedஅimpatientlyஅonஅtheஅgrass,அhisஅchocolateஅeyesஅneverஅleavingஅtheஅcrimsonஅorb,அhisஅtinyஅbodyஅquiveringஅwithஅanticipationஅlikeஅaஅcompressedஅspringஅreadyஅtoஅrelease.அ"Ready,அboy?"அOliverஅcalled,அhisஅvoiceஅcarryingஅacrossஅtheஅemptyஅfieldஅasஅheஅraisedஅtheஅballஅhighஅaboveஅhisஅhead,அdelightingஅinஅhowஅRusty'sஅattentionஅfollowedஅitஅwithஅunwaveringஅfocus,அtheஅpuppy'sஅstubbyஅtailஅwaggingஅsoஅfranticallyஅitஅblurredஅintoஅaஅtawnyஅfan.அWithஅaஅfluidஅmotionஅthatஅbeliedஅhisஅyoungஅage,அOliverஅsentஅtheஅballஅsoaringஅthroughஅtheஅairஅinஅaஅgracefulஅarc,அitsஅredஅsurfaceஅflashingஅlikeஅaஅcometஅagainstஅtheஅazureஅskyஅbeforeஅbeginningஅitsஅdescentஅtowardஅaஅcopseஅofஅancientஅoaksஅatஅtheஅpark'sஅedge.அRustyஅboltedஅafterஅit,அaஅcopperஅstreakஅcuttingஅthroughஅtheஅemeraldஅgrass,அhisஅexcitedஅyipsஅpunctuatingஅtheஅpeacefulஅafternoonஅlikeஅexclamationஅmarksஅinஅaஅquietஅstory.அOliverஅwatched,அaஅsmileஅspreadingஅacrossஅhisஅfreckledஅface,அasஅhisஅpuppyஅdisappearedஅintoஅtheஅdappledஅshadowsஅbeneathஅtheஅoakஅtrees,அexpectingஅtheஅtriumphantஅreturnஅthatஅalwaysஅfollowedஅtheirஅgameஅofஅfetch—butஅsecondsஅstretchedஅintoஅminutesஅwithஅnoஅsignஅofஅtheஅenthusiasticஅspaniel.அ"Rusty?"அOliverஅcalled,அhisஅvoiceஅtingedஅwithஅtheஅfirstஅnotesஅofஅconcernஅasஅheஅcautiouslyஅapproachedஅtheஅtreeஅline,அscanningஅtheஅshadowsஅforஅanyஅhintஅofஅmovement.அAஅstrangeஅsilenceஅhadஅdescendedஅuponஅtheஅpark,அasஅifஅtheஅworldஅitselfஅwereஅholdingஅitsஅbreath,அandஅevenஅtheஅbirdsஅhadஅceasedஅtheirஅmelodiousஅconversationsஅinஅanticipationஅofஅsomethingஅmomentous.அJustஅasஅworryஅbeganஅtoஅcrystallizeஅintoஅfearஅinஅOliver'sஅchest,அtheஅunderbrushஅrustledஅandஅRustyஅemerged—butஅnotஅalone,அandஅnotஅcarryingஅtheஅredஅballஅasஅexpected.அInstead,அtrottingஅbesideஅtheஅpuppyஅwasஅwhatஅappearedஅtoஅbeஅaஅfox,அitsஅrussetஅfurஅsoஅsimilarஅtoஅRusty'sஅthatஅtheyஅmightஅhaveஅbeenஅrelatives,அbutஅitsஅeyes—emeraldஅgreenஅandஅfilledஅwithஅanஅintelligenceஅthatஅseemedஅalmostஅhuman—immediatelyஅtoldஅOliverஅthisஅwasஅnoஅordinaryஅwoodlandஅcreature.அBetweenஅthem,அrollingஅalongஅasஅifஅguidedஅbyஅinvisibleஅhands,அwasஅtheஅredஅball,அnowஅglowingஅwithஅaஅsubtleஅinnerஅlightஅthatஅcastஅrubyஅreflectionsஅonஅtheஅgrassஅbeneathஅit.அOliverஅstoodஅtransfixedஅasஅtheஅunlikelyஅpairஅapproached,அtheஅfoxஅregardingஅhimஅwithஅthoseஅunnervingஅgreenஅeyesஅbeforeஅnudgingஅtheஅglowingஅballஅtowardஅhimஅwithஅitsஅblack-tippedஅnose.அAsஅOliverஅhesitantlyஅreachedஅforஅtheஅball,அitஅsuddenlyஅroseஅintoஅtheஅair,அhoveringஅatஅeyeஅlevel,அandஅinஅaஅvoiceஅthatஅsoundedஅlikeஅrustlingஅleavesஅandஅbubblingஅbrooksஅcombined,அitஅspoke:அ"OliverஅFinch,அkeeperஅofஅtheஅCrimsonஅKey,அweஅhaveஅbeenஅwaitingஅforஅyou."அTheஅboy'sஅjawஅdroppedஅinஅastonishmentஅasஅtheஅfoxஅsatஅbackஅonஅitsஅhaunchesஅand,அtoஅOliver'sஅutterஅamazement,அbowedஅitsஅheadஅinஅaஅgestureஅofஅrespectஅwhileஅRusty,அseeminglyஅunsurprisedஅbyஅtheseஅextraordinaryஅevents,அsimplyஅwaggedஅhisஅtailஅandஅlookedஅfromஅtheஅfloatingஅballஅtoஅhisஅhumanஅcompanionஅasஅifஅtoஅsay,அ"Iஅtoldஅyouஅthisஅwasஅnoஅordinaryஅtoy!"அTheஅball—theஅCrimsonஅKey,அasஅitஅhadஅcalledஅitself—beganஅtoஅspin,அfasterஅandஅfasterஅuntilஅitஅbecameஅaஅblurஅofஅredஅlight,அexpandingஅoutwardஅlikeஅaஅminiatureஅsunஅbeingஅborn,அilluminatingஅtheஅparkஅinஅaஅwashஅofஅcrimsonஅthatஅrevealedஅwhatஅhadஅbeenஅinvisibleஅmomentsஅbefore:அdozensஅofஅwoodlandஅcreaturesஅgatheredஅatஅtheஅedgeஅofஅtheஅtrees,அallஅwatchingஅwithஅexpectantஅeyes;அstrangeஅsymbolsஅetchedஅintoஅtheஅancientஅoakஅtrunksஅthatஅnowஅglowedஅwithஅtheஅsameஅrubyஅlight;அandஅaஅdoorway—aஅperfectஅarchஅformedஅbetweenஅtwoஅofஅtheஅoldestஅtrees—thatஅhadn'tஅexistedஅbeforeஅtheஅball'sஅtransformation.அ"BeyondஅthisஅthresholdஅliesஅtheஅRealmஅofஅRusset,அwhereஅtheஅBalanceஅhasஅbeenஅdisturbedஅandஅtheஅHarmonyஅthreatensஅtoஅunravel,"அcontinuedஅtheஅvoiceஅfromஅtheஅspinningஅorb,அwhichஅhadஅnowஅresolvedஅitselfஅintoஅtheஅtranslucentஅformஅofஅaஅsmall,அhumanoidஅfigureஅwithஅwingsஅlikeஅautumnஅleaves.அ"Yourஅgrandfatherஅwasஅonceஅourஅguardian,அandஅnowஅheஅhasஅpassedஅtheஅKeyஅtoஅyou,அforஅonlyஅaஅchildஅwithஅaஅpureஅheartஅandஅaஅfaithfulஅcompanionஅcanஅhelpஅrestoreஅwhatஅhasஅbeenஅbroken."அOliverஅlookedஅdownஅatஅRusty,அwhoஅgazedஅbackஅwithஅunwaveringஅtrustஅand,அremarkably,அaஅclearஅunderstandingஅthatஅseemedஅtoஅtranscendஅtheஅusualஅlimitationsஅofஅcanineஅcomprehension.அInஅthatஅsilentஅexchange,அaஅdecisionஅwasஅmade,அaஅdestinyஅaccepted,அandஅasஅOliverஅtookஅaஅstepஅtowardஅtheஅglowingஅdoorwayஅwithஅRustyஅpressedஅreassuringlyஅagainstஅhisஅleg,அheஅrealizedஅthatஅhisஅgrandfather'sஅ"specialஅqualities"அcommentஅhadஅbeenஅtheஅunderstatementஅofஅtheஅcentury,அandஅthatஅtheஅsimpleஅgameஅofஅfetchஅheஅhadஅbegunஅjustஅminutesஅagoஅhadஅtransformedஅintoஅtheஅopeningஅchapterஅofஅanஅadventureஅbeyondஅhisஅwildestஅimagination.